<span class="mw-default-size" typeof="mw:File/Frameless"><a href="/wiki/File:Anthony_Giddens_at_the_Progressive_Governance_Converence,_Budapest,_Hungary,_2004_October.jpg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/05/Anthony_Giddens_at_the_Progressive_Governance_Converence%2C_Budapest%2C_Hungary%2C_2004_October.jpg/250px-Anthony_Giddens_at_the_Progressive_Governance_Converence%2C_Budapest%2C_Hungary%2C_2004_October.jpg" decoding="async" width="250" height="311" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/05/Anthony_Giddens_at_the_Progressive_Governance_Converence%2C_Budapest%2C_Hungary%2C_2004_October.jpg/500px-Anthony_Giddens_at_the_Progressive_Governance_Converence%2C_Budapest%2C_Hungary%2C_2004_October.jpg 1.5x" data-file-width="1329" data-file-height="1652"></a></span><div class="infobox-caption">Giddens in 2004</div>
