<li>Beck, Ulrich; Giddens, Anthony; Lash, Scott (1994) <i>Reflexive Modernization: Politics, Tradition and Aesthetics in the Modern Social Order</i>. Cambridge: <a href="/wiki/Polity_(publisher)" title="Polity (publisher)">Polity</a>.</li>
